    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Party Spirits是一款在线多人派对游戏，在这里你可以和多达6名玩家一起参与混乱而紧凑的迷你游戏，证明你配得上获得新生的机会。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>独特的基于物理效果的迷你游戏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跳到其他玩家身上、摧毁桥梁、在跷跷板上保持平衡，还有更多有趣的互动！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112210/extras/7b2df424e5a1a3ad5dc23733184add48.poster.avif?t=1733501205\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112210/extras/7b2df424e5a1a3ad5dc23733184add48.webm?t=1733501205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112210/extras/7b2df424e5a1a3ad5dc23733184add48.mp4?t=1733501205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>死亡后继续影响游戏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仅仅观看太无聊了！利用专为每个迷你游戏设计的独特死后机制来影响比赛的结果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112210/extras/0de11e05f9f63718e76fbf6d26d6bd8d.poster.avif?t=1733501205\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112210/extras/0de11e05f9f63718e76fbf6d26d6bd8d.webm?t=1733501205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112210/extras/0de11e05f9f63718e76fbf6d26d6bd8d.mp4?t=1733501205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>个性化定制</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过特殊效果和一首独特的旋律、歌曲或圣歌，增强你的迷你游戏胜利体验。这些效果只能通过游戏获得。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112210/extras/521c3e8e2ef244e2aad338398db1960f.poster.avif?t=1733501205\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112210/extras/521c3e8e2ef244e2aad338398db1960f.webm?t=1733501205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112210/extras/521c3e8e2ef244e2aad338398db1960f.mp4?t=1733501205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
